	<span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span><span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><strong></strong></span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>嘉宾简介</strong>：</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 刘老师出生于吉林省吉林市，1986年毕业于东北师范大学，获文学硕士学位；2000年毕业于日本京都大学，获文学博士学位。曾任职于清华大学思想文化研究所，现为清华大学历史系教授、博士生导师，并担任中国日本史学会日本古代史分会会长，中国民俗学会副会长、中华日本哲学会副会长等多项社会职务。</span> 
</p>
<p align="center">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/11/12/u5dca486260a9f.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="472" /> 
</p>
<p>
	<span style="line-height:2;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 刘老师主要从事日本史、中日文化交流史等领域的研究工作，先后撰写、出版了《东亚的时间：岁时文化的比较研究》《日本的面孔》《端午》等多部学术专著，并在《历史研究》《清华大学学报》《华中师范大学学报》等学术期刊发表论文数十篇。</span> 
</p>
<p align="center">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/11/12/u5dca48d181a50.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="430" /><img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/11/12/u5dca48b34bf2b.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="432" /> 
</p>
<p align="center">
	<img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/11/12/u5dca48e476909.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="287" /><img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/11/12/u5dca48f618ac6.jpg" alt="" width="190" height="287" /><img src="/Uploads/Picture/2019/11/12/u5dca490517556.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="290" /> 
</p>
